<script lang="ts">
import { Component, Vue } from 'vue-property-decorator'
import { AuthModule } from '@/store/modules/authentication.module'
import { DisplayModule } from '@/store/modules/display.module'
import { store } from '@/store/index'
import { clickOutside } from '@/directives/v-click-outside/index'
 
@Component({
  directives: {
    clickOutside
  }
})
export default class Header extends Vue {
  blocksShow = {
    menu: false,
    location: false,
    user: false
  };
 
  toggleRegistrationPopup () {
    store.dispatch('display/toggleRegistration')
  }
 
  logIn () {
    store.dispatch('auth/login')
  }
 
  clearSearchInput () {
    const inputDesktop = this.$refs.searchInputDesktop as HTMLInputElement
    if (inputDesktop) {
      inputDesktop.value = ''
    }
 
    const inputMobile = this.$refs.searchInputMobile as HTMLInputElement
    if (inputMobile) {
      inputMobile.value = ''
    }
  }
 
  get loggedIn () {
    return AuthModule.logged
  }
 
  get userName () {
    return AuthModule.name.length > 10
      ? AuthModule.name.substring(0, 10) + '...'
      : AuthModule.name
  }
 
  logout () {
    store.dispatch('auth/logout')
  }
 
  toggleMainMenu () {
    setTimeout(() => {
      this.blocksShow.menu = !this.blocksShow.menu
    })
  }
 
  closeMainMenu () {
    this.blocksShow.menu = false
  }
 
  toggleUserMenu () {
    setTimeout(() => {
      this.blocksShow.user = !this.blocksShow.user
    })
  }
 
  closeUserMenu () {
    this.blocksShow.user = false
  }
  mounted () {
    store.dispatch('auth/actualizeUser')
  }
}
</script>
